# Project Fix Walkthrough

I have successfully analyzed the project, identified multiple critical issues, and applied fixes. Use this guide to understand the changes and verify the project state.

## 🛠️ Changes Made

### 1. Dependency & Configuration Fixes
- **Solved Build Failures**: Performed a clean installation of dependencies and rebuilt `sharp`, which was causing the build to fail.
- **Fixed Linting**: incompatible `lint` script in [package.json](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/package.json) was updated.
- **Missing Dependencies**: Installed `@eslint/js`, `globals`, and `typescript-eslint` to fix the broken ESLint configuration.

### 2. Code Improvements
- **Optimized [HeroSlider.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/components/HeroSlider.tsx)**: Moved the static `slides` array outside the component to prevent unnecessary re-creation on every render, improving performance. Used proper `ReturnType<typeof setTimeout>` to fix TypeScript errors.
- **Removed Dead Code**: Deleted redundant usage of `<NavigateWithScroll />` in [AppRoutes.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/src/routes/AppRoutes.tsx) which was causing potential scroll conflicts.

